title: Eclipse Fill 03 (Strike!, Masked Man, Prowler, Zooniverse)
description:
Too much alcohol, not enough pot - must be time for Eclipse Fill Part 3!!

Tonight's players:

Strike! 1-6 and Strike! vs Sgt. Strike Special - African-American teen takes over for war-time hero. Chuck Dixon writes.

Masked Man 1-12 - BC Boyer does his riff on the Spirit.

The Prowler 1-4 and White Zombie - Tim Truman and John K. Snyder III pay homage to the Spider.

Zooniverse 1-6 - Fil Barlow plays with aliens!


My most profound thanks to the creative teams and the creative scanners! Procure 'em, proselytize them!
